snippet.title: Concord - Launch Trailer I PS5 & PC Games
snippet.description:
Concord is Available Now on PS5 and PC*.

Rally your crew and begin your adventure across the Concord Galaxy with 16 Freegunners, 12 Maps and 6 PVP Modes. Earn hundreds of rewards for your Freegunners and unlock variants to expand your playstyle. 

To stay up to date, follow @PlayConcord on social media.

*Account for PlayStation™Network and internet connection required. Paid for PlayStation®Plus membership (sold separately) required on PS5.

#ps5 #ps5games #pcgames #concord
